title: jetAudio Music Player Plus 5.2.0 APK
description:
jetAudio loses virtually all digital music files (.wav, .mp3, .ogg, .flac, .m4a, .mpc, .tta, .wv, .ape, .mod, .spx, .wma * et al.). Besides, jetAudio provides high-quality sound and offers a wide range of sound effects such as stereo widening (X-Wide), Reverb (Reverb) and the bass boost (X-Bass). jetAudio offers 32 preset for the equalizer, through which you can achieve sound for every taste. And for those who want to achieve a particular sound, there is a 10- or 20-band graphic equalizer, as well as additional playback settings, including playback speed control, a smooth transition between tracks (Crossfade), AGC, and more. Features Basic version and Plus:

Features available only in the version Plus:

10-band graphic equalizer with 32 presets.
Wide, Reverb, X-Bass sound effects.
AGC (Automatic Gain Control) Used to avoid volume changes between tracks.
A change of pace or speed (0,5x and 2x)
Crossfading, Gap-less play.
Fade-in / Fade-out effects.
Browse and play music from the artits, albums, songs, playlists and folders.
Balance of sound and volume control.
24-hour sleep timer.
The ability to send status on Facebook and Twitter that you are listening.
The ability to show that playing at the moment.
Key switches
Support for large formats
